{"books":[{"id":"jfjb","name":"解放军报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"dates":[{"year":1964,"month":1,"day":16}],"page_start":4,"page_end":4,"description":"","is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"title":"春雷，在巴拿马响起——献给斗争中的巴拿马人民","authors":["周纲辰生"],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九六四年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"第一声春雷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在巴拿马响起！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巴拿马呵，巴拿马运河区，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是谁的土地？！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她不是密西西比河的支流，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她不是加利福尼亚的水渠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巴拿马人民的血泪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浮起了海盗的船舰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"涂染了美国的花旗；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巴拿马七万死难者的白骨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"垒起了殖民者的高楼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"筑起了运河的长堤！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巴拿马运河，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"流过巴拿马的土地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巴拿马运河，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是巴拿马人民的！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为甚么巴拿马人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"掬饮自己的河水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要向华尔街的大亨纳税？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为甚么巴拿马人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不能看见祖国的天空，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飘扬着自己的国旗？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自己的路不能走，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自己的家不能息，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自己的天空、河流和土地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不能自由地歌唱和呼吸！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美国的强权，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枪杀了协议；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美国的铁丝网，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"囚禁了公理；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美国的皮靴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"踩着巴拿马的尊严；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美国的刺刀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挑着巴拿马的独立！……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵！巴拿马，血的巴拿马，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"六十年了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我听见过你在呐喊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我听见过你在哭泣！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是漫长的忍耐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"聚集了仇恨的旋风；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是如山的苦难，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爆发了白热的岩浆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冲天的火炬！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“死亡的河岸”复活了！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从中美洲昂首站立！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"血的浪头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炸响了第一声春雷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二十个人倒下去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"百多万巴拿马人民一齐站起！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"整个巴拿马一齐站起。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亚洲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"非洲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拉丁美洲……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"漫天沉雷吼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"遍地风云急！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巴拿马呀，我们支援你！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美帝国主义，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坏事做了千万件，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"血债积下千万笔。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在朝鲜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它杀死多少阿妈妮！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在日本，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它蛮横霸占不讲理！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在台湾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它扶持僵尸蒋介石！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在古巴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它要把这个国家窒息！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它在老挝纵火，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它在南越放毒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它又要把第七舰队开进印度洋里！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这一切，这一切啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全世界人民，不会饶它，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不会忘记！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全世界人民联合起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战斗！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"反抗！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冲击！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"起来呀，受苦受难的兄弟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"起来呀，饥寒交迫的奴隶！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就是拳头对刺刀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"石头迎弹雨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们也要——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"反抗到底！战斗到底！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世界上，只有人民的力量，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才不可抗拒！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世界上，只有人民的团结，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才真正无与匹敌！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听呵，巴拿马的怒吼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"已经响彻大地！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听呵，斗争的春雷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"已经震撼天宇！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"华尔街的摩天高楼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"便是绝好的绞架，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怒涛滚滚的大西洋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"便是绝好的坟地。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巴拿马人民，全世界人民，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快快拉紧绞索，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用力！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用力！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用力！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们要把斗争进行到底！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要巴拿马，不要美国佬！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"辰生作"}],"alias":""},"tags":[{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}